dc_title_s: South America, Venezuela, approaches to Puerto Cabello (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours. "From U.S. Navy surveys to 1940 and Venezuelan charts to 1979." Place names in Spanish with glossary in English. "Copyright 1994 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Inset: El Palito and Morón. Scale 1:25,000. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 24453. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dct_spatial_sm: Paria, Gulf of (Venezuela and Trinidad and Tobago)
